Series marking the 75th anniversary of the beginning of the Blitz. Celebrities explore the Blitz history of their home cities.

 

London 
1/5 Shane Richie travels around his home city of London to learn about the Blitz.

Liverpool 
2/5 Liverpool actor Ricky Tomlinson look at the effect the Blitz had on his home city.

Norwich 
3/5 Myleene Klass looks into the story of the Baedeker Blitz on Norwich. 

Cardiff 
4/5 John Humphrys returns to South Wales to discover the history of the Blitz there. 

Birmingham 
5/5 David Harewood travels back to his native Birmingham to look at his city's Blitz story.
